<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Go to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Inventory management &gt; Periodic tasks &gt; Closing and adjustment</strong> or <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Inventory management &gt; Periodic tasks &gt; Closing and adjustment in currency</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">On the Action Pane, select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">Adjustment &gt; Wizard</strong>.</p>
</li>
