<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="56"><strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="56">Transactions</strong> – Adjust transactions.</li>
</ul>
