<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Next</strong>. Either the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Select on-hand inventory</strong> page or the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Adjust transactions</strong> page appears, depending on the method of adjustment that you selected.</p>
