<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">If you know that both positive and negative adjustments will be made during the cost adjustment, this procedure should be completed in two separate stages: positive adjustment and negative adjustment.</p>
