</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="179"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="179">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="179">Balance from ledger account or dimensions</strong> page, set the following fields:</p>
