</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="205"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="205">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="205">Select on-hand inventory</strong> page, set the following fields:</p>
