<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="207">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="207">Parameters</strong> FastTab, set the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="207">Warehouse</strong> option to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-inventory-adjustment-wizard.md" sourcestartlinenumber="207">Yes</strong>.</li>
